
"I'm not okay."
Alpha Acis Crostin has seen too much. He distances himself from everyone to avoid giving hurt and getting hurt. After the funeral of his best friend and head pack warrior during a raging war, Acis stumbles across his mate, who eerily resembles his past lover. Determined to stay away from her, he rejects her, only to find out that their fate is one that was complicatedly tangled from the start...